
General:
    - ctrl + e                  ->  view recent files
    - ctrl + Enter              ->  intention action / quick fix
    - ctrl + r                  ->  search and replace item(s)

Selection:
    - ctrl + shift + alt + j    ->  select all occurrences
    - shift + alt + Click       ->  multiple carets

Formatting:
    - ctrl + shift + alt + l    ->  auto format window